 the inverse Compton emission from electrons and\nalso the pion decay emission from protons, mostly by shifting their cut-off\nenergies to respectively lower and higher energies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 3 May 2014 17:54:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-19"}
