 designed for the\nhalf-filled Hubbard model on the honeycomb lattice ([Giuliani, A. and V.\nMastropietro, Commun. Math. Phys. 293 (2010), 301-346]).\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 May 2014 06:43:35 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 19 Aug 2014 11:51:18 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 30 Aug 2015 07:51:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-09-01"}
