se\nfunction only depends on the crystal configuration, so the method could be\nextended to any PET scanners with the same detector crystal configuration.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 4 May 2014 07:10:43 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 17 Jun 2014 10:08:24 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Thu, 11 Sep 2014 10:52:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-12"}
